 & =\frac{L_{ACS}^{n\#,ik}}{L_{ACS}^{n,i}}\times L_{IRS}^{n,i}\times\frac{L_{CPS}^{ij,ik}}{L_{CPS}^{i\#,ik}}
\end{align*}

